OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy who stabbed another
OL,7,Fteenager through the heart on the way
OL,8,Fhome from school has been named
OL,9,Fpublicly for the first time.
OL,11,FAlfie Lewis, 15, was stabbed to death
OL,12,Fin front of pupils leaving a primary
OL,13,Fschool in the Horsforth area of Leeds
OL,14,Flast November.
OL,16,FSchoolboy Bardia Shojaeifard, who was
OL,17,F14 at the time, was found guilty of
OL,18,Fmurdering Alfie by a Leeds Crown Court
OL,19,Fjury in April.
