OL,6,FShojaeifard can be named publicly for
OL,7,Fthe first time after Mr Justice
OL,8,FCotter, sitting at Leeds Crown Court
OL,9,Fon Friday, lifted reporting
OL,10,Frestrictions preventing him from being
OL,11,Fidentified.
OL,13,FHe said lifting the defendant's
OL,14,Fanonymity would help in the "vitally
OL,15,Fimportant debate about the scourge of
OL,16,Fknife crime, among young people in
OL,17,Fparticular".
