OL,6,FThe judge said: "The crime he
OL,7,Fcommitted was extraordinary...Alfie
OL,8,FLewis was attacked as he tried to calm
OL,9,FShojaeifard. The shocking assault was
OL,10,Fwitnessed by a large amount of people.
OL,12,F"I have no doubt it sent shock waves
OL,13,Facross the local community but more
OL,14,Fwidely. Put simply, many must have
OL,15,Fbeen and still asking the question how
OL,16,Fit comes to pass a young man such as
OL,17,Fthis carries and uses a knife in these
OL,18,Fcircumstances and how the scourge of
OL,19,Fknife crime permeates or youth until
OL,20,Fmore is done about it...J"How bad have
OL,21,Fthings become?
